by throws his support to Adam Cote in race for governor |last=Collins |first=Steve |date=June 4, 2018 |work=[[Lewiston Sun Journal]] |access-date=June 4, 2018}}</ref>\n* [[Colleen Madigan]], state representative<ref name=\"CoteEndorsements\"/>\n* [[Anne-Marie Mastraccio]], state representative<ref name=\"CoteEndorsements\"/>\n* [[Patrick K. McGowan]], former state representative, candidate for Governor in [[Maine gubernatorial election, 2010|2010]], nominee for [[Maine's 2nd congressional district|ME-02]] in [[United States House of Representatives elections, 1990|1990]] and [[United States House of Representatives elections, 1992|1992]], former [[Small Business Administration]] Regional Administrator<ref name=\"CoteEndorsements\"/>\n* Cynthia Mehnert, [[Orono, Maine|Orono]] Town Councillor<ref name=\"CoteEndorsements\"/>\n* Cecil Munson, Former [[Augusta, Maine|Augusta]] City Councillor<ref name=\"CoteEndorsements\"/>\n* Kevin O'Connell, [[Brewer, Maine|Brewer]] City Councillor<ref name=\"CoteEndorsements\"/>\n* Peter O'Donnell, former [[Mayor of Portland, Maine|Mayor of Portland]]<ref name=\"CoteEndorsements\"/>\n* Patrick Paradis, former state representative and former [[Augusta, Maine|Augusta]] City Councillor<ref name=\"CoteEndorsements\"/>\n* Josh Plourde, former [[Bangor, Maine|Bangor]] City Councillor<ref name=\"CoteEndorsements\"/>\n* Christina Riley, state representative<ref name=\"CoteEndorsements\"/>\n* David Rollins, Mayor of [[Augusta, Maine|Augusta]]<ref name=\"CoteEndorsements\"/>\n* Michael Sanphy, Mayor of [[Westbrook, Maine|Westbrook]]<ref name=\"CoteEndorsements\"/>\n* [[Stephen Stanley]], state representative<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://bangordailynews.com/2018/03/06/opinion/contributors/adam-cote-is-the-leader-rural-maine-needs/ |title=Adam Cote is the leader rural Maine needs |last=Stanley |first=Stephen S. |date=March 6, 2018 |work=[[Bangor Daily News]] |access-date=March 9, 2018}}</ref>\n* Spencer Thibodeau, [[Portland, Maine City Council|P