idende]] | date=2016-02-21 | accessdate=2016-03-15}}</ref>\n* '''22''' \u2013 [[Sonny James]] (87), American country music singer-songwriter.<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://www.tennessean.com/story/entertainment/music/2016/02/22/country-music-hall-famer-sonny-james-dead-86/80556058/?from=global&sessionKey=&autologin= |title=Country singer Sonny James dies at 87 |website=Tennessean.com |date=2016-02-22 |accessdate=2016-04-22}}</ref>\n* '''29''' \u2013 [[Josefin Nilsson]] (46), Swedish singer.<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.svt.se/nyheter/lokalt/ost/josefin-nilsson-ar-dod | title=Josefin Nilsson \u00e4r d\u00f6d | first=Carl Bruno | last=Tersmeden | language=Swedish |work=[[Fyens Stiftstidende]] | date=2016-02-29 | accessdate=2016-03-15}}</ref>\n\n===March===\n* '''3''' \u2013 [[Gavin Christopher]], 66, American R&B singer-songwriter and producer<ref>[http://www.soultracks.com/story-gavin-christopher-dies \"One Step Closer To You\" singer Gavin Christopher dies]</ref>\n* '''8''' \u2013 [[George Martin]], (90), English producer.<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.cnn.com/videos/entertainment/2016/03/09/sir-george-martin-obituary.cnn |title=Sir George Martin dies at 90}}</ref>\n* '''9'''\n** [[Ray Griff]] (75), Canadian country singer-songwriter, (aspiration pneumonia).<ref>{{cite web|url=https://calgaryherald.com/entertainment/music/legendary-calgary-country-gentleman-ray-griff-dies-at-the-age-of-75|title=Legendary Calgary 'country gentleman' Ray Griff dies at the age of 75|work=[[Calgary Herald]]|date=March 11, 2016}}</ref>\n** [[Nan\u00e1 Vasconcelos]] (71), Brazilian percussionist.<ref>{{cite news | url=http://jazztimes.com/articles/171730-brazilian-percussionist-nan-vasconcelos-dies-at-71 | title=Brazilian Percussionist Nan\u00e1 Vasconcelos Dies at 71 | last=Jeff | first=Tamarkin | work=[[JazzTimes]] | date=2016-03-09 | accessdate=2016-03-15}}</ref>\n* '''10''' \n**[[Keith Emerson]] (71), English pianist and keyboardist ([[Emerson, Lake & Palmer]]).<ref>{{cite