ne Pashley, Olympic athlete and opera singer \u2013 obituary]</ref>\n* '''8''' \u2013 [[Don Ciccone]] (70), American singer-songwriter and musician ([[The Critters]], [[The Four Seasons (band)|The Four Seasons]], [[Tommy James and the Shondells]]).<ref>[http://www.legacy.com/obituaries/latimes/obituary.aspx?n=don-ciccone&pid=181823950 Obituary: Don Ciccone 1946 \u2013 2016]</ref>\n* '''9'''\n** [[Bored Nothing]] (26), Australian musician, suicide.<ref>[http://www.abc.net.au/news/2016-10-13/bored-nothing-aka-fergus-miller-dies-aged-26/7928412 Bored Nothing, Melbourne musician Fergus Miller, dies aged 26 after battle with depression]</ref>\n** [[Michiyuki Kawashima]] (47), Japanese musician ([[Boom Boom Satellites]]), brain tumor.<ref>[http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-10-11/boom-boom-satellites-vocalist-michiyuki-kawashima-passes-away/.107487 Boom Boom Satellites' Vocalist Michiyuki Kawashima Passes Away]</ref>\n** [[Quique Lucca]] (103), Puerto Rican musician, founder of [[La Sonora Ponce\u00f1a]].<ref>[http://www.elnuevodia.com/entretenimiento/musica/nota/falleceelcreadordelasonoraponcenaquiquelucca-2249714/ Fallece el creador de La Sonora Ponce\u00f1a Quique Lucca] {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n** {{Interlanguage link multi|Guy Nadon (drummer)|fr|3=Guy Nadon (batteur)|lt=Guy Nadon}}, (82), Canadian jazz drummer.<ref>[http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/guy-nadon-quebec-king-of-drums-dies-1.3798322 'King of drums' Guy Nadon dies at 82]</ref>\n** {{Interlanguage link multi|Marin Petrache Pechea|ro}} (71), Romanian jazz musician, cancer.<ref>[http://www.antena3.ro/timp-liber/muzica/a-murit-celebrul-muzician-marin-petrache-pechea-380493.html A murit cunoscutul muzician Marin Pechea Petrache] {{in lang|ro}}</ref>\n* '''10''' \u2013 [[Issa Bagayogo]],= (54), Malian musician.<ref>[http://www.maliweb.net/musique/musique-malienne-deuil-issa-bagayogo-dit-techno-issa-tire-reverence-1823152.html Malian music in mourning: Techno Issa Issa Bagayogo said bows]</ref>\n* '''11'