audian family tree}}\nThe emperors from [[Augustus]] to [[Commodus]] can be organised into one large family tree.\n\n{{familytree/start}}\n{{familytree | | | | | | | | | | | | | Aug | | | | | | Tno\n |Aug = '''[[Augustus]]'''<br>63 BC \u2013 27 BC \u2013 AD 14{{sfn|Everitt|2007|pp=9, 208, 313}}\n |Tno = [[Tiberius Claudius Nero (praetor 42 BC)|Tiberius Claudius Nero]]<br>85\u201333 BC{{sfn|Everitt|2007|p=125}}}}\n{{familytree | | | | | | | | | | | | | |!| | | |,|-|-|-|^|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|.|}}\n{{familytree | | | | | | | | | Mva |v| Jul |-| Tib | | | | | | | | | | | | | | Ncd |Jul=[[Julia the Elder]]<br>39 BC \u2013 AD 14{{sfn|Everitt|2007|pp=xviii, xxiii}} |Tib='''[[Tiberius]]'''<br>42 BC \u2013 AD 14\u201337{{sfn|Everitt|2007|pp=xviii, xxiii}} |Ncd=[[Nero Claudius Drusus]]<br>38\u20139 BC{{sfn|Everitt|2007|pp=xviii, xxi}} |Mva=[[Marcus Vipsanius Agrippa]]<br>63\u201312 BC{{sfn|Everitt|2007|pp=xvi, xxi}}}}\n{{familytree | | | | | |,|-|-|-|-|-|^|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|.| | | |)|-|-|-|.|}}\n{{familytree | Pau |v| Juy | | | | | | | | | | | | | | | | | | | | | | Age |v| Ger | | Cla ||Cla='''[[Claudius]]'''<br>10 BC \u2013 41-54{{sfn|Everitt|2007|pp=xxi, xxiii}} |Ger=[[Germanicus]]<br>16 BC \u2013 AD 19{{sfn|Everitt|2007|pp=xxi, xxiii}} |Age=[[Agrippina the Elder]]<br>14 BC \u2013 AD 33 |Juy=[[Julia the Younger]]<br>19BC \u2013 AD28{{sfn|Everitt|2007|pp=xxx, xxiii}} |Pau=[[Lucius Aemilius Paullus (consul 1)|Lucius Aemilius Paullus]]<br>d. 14 }}\n{{familytree | | | |`|-|.| | | | | | | | | | | | | | | | | | | |,|-|-|-|.| |`|-|v|-|-|-|v|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|.| }}\n{{familytree | Tor |v| Ael | | | | | | | | | | Ves | | | | | | Gdc | | Cae |-| Cal | | Agy |v| Gna | | |!|Cal='''[[Caligula]]'''<br>12-37-41 |Agy=[[Agrippina the Younger]]<br>15\u201359 |Gna=[[Gnaeus Domitius Ahenobarbus (consul 32)|Gnaeus Domitius Ahenobarbus]]<br>17 BC \u2013 AD 40 |Ael=[[Aemilia Lepida (fiancee of Claudius)|Aemilia Lepida]]<br>4 BC \u2013 AD 53 |Tor=[[Marcus Junius Silanus Torquatus (co