ronius Maximus]]'''<br>396-455-455 |Mre=[[Marcia Euphemia]] |Le1='''[[Leo I the Thracian|Leo I]]'''<br>401-457-474 |Ael=[[Verina]]<br>d. 484 |Bas='''[[Basiliscus]]'''<br><small>d. 477<br>'''r.  475-76'''</small> |Ant='''[[Anthemius]]'''<br>420-467-472 |unk=''unknown brother''}}\n{{familytree | |!| | | | | |`|-|-|-|-|-|v|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|.| |`|-|.| | | | | | | | | |!|}}\n{{familytree | unn |-| Nep | | Zen |v| Ari |-| Ana | | Len |-| Mru | | | | Oly |-| Plc |Mru=[[Marcian (usurper)|Marcian]] |Len=[[Leontia Porphyrogenita|Leontia]] |Ari=[[Ariadne (empress)|Ariadne]]<br>450\u2013515 |Zen='''[[Zeno (emperor)|Zeno]]'''<br><small>425\u2013491<br>'''r. 474\u2013475, 476\u2013491'''</small> |Ana='''[[Anastasius I (emperor)|Anastasius I]]'''<br>430-491-518 |Oly='''[[Olybrius]]'''<br>430-472-472 |Plc=[[Placidia]] |Nep='''[[Julius Nepos]]'''<br>430-474-480 |unn=''unknown wife''}}\n{{familytree | | | | | | | | | | | |!|}}\n{{familytree | Rom | | | | | | | | Le2 | | Gly |Le2='''[[Leo II (emperor)|Leo II]]'''<br>467-474-474 |Gly='''[[Glycerius]]'''<br>420-473-474-480 |Rom='''[[Romulus Augustus]]'''<br>462-475-476}}\n{{familytree/end}}\n\n==518\u20131453==\n\n{{further|Family tree of the Byzantine emperors}}\n\n==References==\n===Citations===\n{{Reflist}}\n\n===Sources===\n* {{cite book|title=Augustus: the life of Rome's first emperor|last=Everitt|first=Anthony|year=2007|location=New York|publisher=Random House Trade Paperbacks|isbn=9780812970586|ref=harv}}\n\n{{Family trees}}\n\n[[Category:Ancient Roman family trees]]\n[[Category:Roman emperors]]\n[[Category:Roman imperial dynasties]]\n", "name_user": "Agricolae", "label": "safe", "comment": "migrate template", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Family_tree_of_the_Roman_emperors"}
